16 ROS2 - Python Publisher –Square Movement (Improved)

  • Create a ROS Package with Python, Improving the infinite loop of square movement with Action Absolute Rotate

Tips

•ROS Action :
/turtle1/rotate_absolute

•ROS Action interface:
turtlesim/action/RotateAbsolute

ros2 run turtlesim turtlesim_node

•ROS Topic:
/turtle1/cmd_vel

•ROS Data Type:
geometry_msgs/msg/Twist

ros2 node info /turtlesim


ros2 interface show turtlesim/action/RotateAbsolute

Reference : https://docs.ros.org/en/humble/Installation.html
